In a world driven by empathy and the desire to make a lasting impact, a new frontier in philanthropy emerges. Welcome to World3, the app that revolutionizes charitable giving and transforms lives.

Imagine a place where individuals from all corners of the globe unite, driven by a shared purpose – to create a better world for all. World3 empowers you to be the change you wish to see, providing a seamless platform to support causes that resonate with your values and ignite your passion.

With World3, your journey begins with a simple tap. Explore a diverse array of charitable initiatives, spanning across vital sectors such as education, health, and environmental conservation. Each cause bears a profound story, embodying the hopes and dreams of communities in need.

But World3 is more than just a conduit for donations. It is a catalyst for meaningful impact. Through the power of blockchain technology and the integration of Chainlink services like price feed, every contribution becomes an immutable thread woven into the fabric of change. Transparency and accountability are at the core of our values, ensuring that your support reaches its intended destination and makes a tangible difference.

Join a global community of compassionate individuals, united by the belief that small acts of kindness can create extraordinary transformations. Together, we can uplift the marginalized, heal the sick, educate the young, and protect our planet.

Step into a world where generosity knows no boundaries. Embrace the spirit of giving and embark on a journey that transcends borders, cultures, and limitations. World3 – Empowering Humanity, Transforming Lives.


Welcome to World3, the intuitive and user-friendly platform that brings people together to create positive change. On our homepage, you'll find a comprehensive summary of what this application is all about, providing you with a clear understanding of our mission and purpose.

Now, let's dive into the heart of World3—the donation page. Here, you'll discover a curated list of current donation campaigns available on our platform. Although we currently have two active campaigns, rest assured that we're continuously working behind the scenes to bring you more impactful initiatives very soon.

To contribute to any of these worthy causes, simply click on the prominent "Donate" button next to each campaign. By doing so, you'll be redirected to a dedicated page where you can choose the amount you wish to donate. Whether it's $25, $100, $500, or $1000, you have the freedom to select the value that resonates with you. Rest assured that these prices are calculated based on the latest Ethereum (ETH) values converted to USD using our reliable Chainlink price feed service.

At World3, we believe in keeping the donation process simple, transparent, and accessible to all. We strive to create a seamless experience that encourages individuals from diverse backgrounds and user groups to contribute towards making the world a better place.

Now, let's take a quick peek at the admin dashboard, where the magic happens. As an administrator, you have the power to add new donation campaigns. Simply enter the title, description, target amount, start and end dates, select the relevant country, and choose a captivating image that represents the essence of the cause. With just a few clicks, you'll be creating an opportunity for others to join you in making a positive impact on the world.

Together, let's embrace the spirit of giving and transform lives. Join us at World3, where every donation, no matter how small, has the power to make a significant difference. It's time to contribute and create a brighter future for all.

Let's donate today and build a better world.